{
  "stem": "1183.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I looked at every movie from her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "As I said, it was a marvelous time, and the best time of my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In 1938, we moved back to Amsterdam in a new complex of houses, which were very modern for that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was originally kind of a cooperative.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was a very, very nice what you call here a flat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were lived on the first floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My father still-- we moved back to Amsterdam with my father still, apparently, as far as I can recall.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He didn't have too much work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was at that time then unemployed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were on unemployment insurance, which much to the dismay of my mother and father, naturally, who were not used to that and hated every moment of it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was at school, in public school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I went to the public school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The public school I was-- I had to go there, was situated in a very, very, very well-to-do area.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I was still a very provincial girl after five years in Zandvoort.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Naive and trusting, I happened to be in a class where a teacher was, who for some reason or other, didn't like me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I could, as is hindsight now, not sure, but he didn't like me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Everything he tried to degrade-- not degrade me, to humiliate me in front of the class.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But still, I am sorry to say it has left a lasting impression.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And even sometimes to this day, I feel sometimes those effects.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was not good for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I had several accidents in that school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I broke my-- fractured my arm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He had to-- his favorite kids had to walk me to my house, which was quite a distance, which shouldn't have been done.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
